name: Golden Sweet Cornbread from Del Monte®
author: Del Monte
summary: Creamed corn and whole corn kernels bake up moist and sweet in this easy cornbread recipe using corn muffin mix  – enjoy as muffins or squares with anything from chili to holiday meals.
ingredients: 1 (14.75 ounce) can Del Monte® Sweet Corn Cream Style, No Salt Added
1 (15.25 ounce) can DEL MONTE® Whole Kernel Corn, No Salt Added, well drained
directions: Coat a glass or metal 9-inch square baking dish with non-stick cooking spray
Stir together all ingredients in a large mixing bowl; batter will be slightly lumpy
Pour batter evenly into prepared pan
Bake 40 to 45 minutes or until deep golden brown and wooden pick inserted in center comes out clean
